SUMMARY:Art Meets Jazz: Brandee Younger
DESCRIPTION:Art Meets Jazz returns for its eighth installment in this annual performance series. This year’s program features two-time Grammy–nominated harpist and composer Brandee Younger\, whose work continues to expand the role of the harp in contemporary jazz and popular music. \nHer latest release\, Gadabout Season\, is her third album for the legendary Impulse! label. Younger is an NAACP Image Award winner and a recipient of the 2025 Doris Duke Artist Award\, the largest prize in the United States dedicated to individual artists. Her collaborations span genres and generations\, including work with Pharoah Sanders\, Ravi Coltrane\, Christian McBride\, John Legend\, The Roots\, and Beyoncé. \nYour ticket includes a wine and food reception beginning at 6 p.m.\, with catering provided by Montclair’s own MOSO Signature. \nArt Meets Jazz is presented by the Montclair Art Museum’s African American Cultural Committee (AACC). \nMust be 21+ to attend. \n\nSponsorship:\n\n$2\,000–Celestial Sponsor\n\nPrivate\, center orchestra table seating for 4\, meet-and-greet opportunity with the artist\, special Art Meets Jazz event gift bag\, and more\n\n\n$1\,200–Angel Sponsor\n\nPrivate orchestra table seating for 4\, meet-and-greet opportunity with the artist\, and more\n\n\n$600–Harp Sponsor\n\nPremium orchestra seating for 2\, meet-and-greet opportunity with the artist\, and more\n\n\n$300-Muse Sponsor\n\nPremium orchestra seating for 1\, meet and greet opportunity with the artist\, and more\n\n\n\nFor more info on sponsorship benefits click here. \nPURCHASE SPONSORSHIPS HERE \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/art-meets-jazz-brandee-younger/
LOCATION:Montclair Art Museum\, 3 South Mountain Ave\, Montclair\, NJ\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Live Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Brandee-Younger.jpg
