SUMMARY:CreativeMornings: Simon Galperin
DESCRIPTION:CreativeMornings is a free monthly breakfast lecture series for anyone who identifies as creative (yes\, that means you!). With 250+ chapters in 70 countries\, we’re thrilled to host the first & only NJ chapter in Montclair! \nThis month\, our global theme is “Local” and our speaker is Simon Galperin. Simon is the founder and Executive Editor of The Jersey Bee\, a nonprofit local news organization in Essex County that helps working-class communities and communities of color access resources\, build connections\, and participate in civic life. His work blends human-centered design\, journalism\, and technology to help people navigate – and improve – the systems that shape daily life. \nCan’t wait to see you there! \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/creativemornings-simon-galperin/
LOCATION:RecRoom\, 1 Lackawanna Plaza\, Ste. 6\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art & Culture,Community,General Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/creativemornings-2.2026-1.png
