SUMMARY:Consumer Fraud Presentation
DESCRIPTION:On March 23 at 12pm at the Montclair Public Library\, the Office of Assemblywoman Rosaura “Rosy” Bagolie will be holding a Consumer Fraud Presentation. The office will be hosting a speaker from the Division of Consumer Affairs to give a presentation on how to avoid falling susceptible to different types of scams. This event will provide valuable information to help Montclair residents stay safe from dangerous forms of fraud. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
